        "title": "Alaska Air Group and Bank of America Expand Long-Standing Credit Card Partnership",
        "description": "",
        "summary": "Alaska Air Group Inc. (NYSE: ALK) and Bank of America (NYSE: BAC) today announced a multi-year extension of their co-branded credit card agreement – a continuation of the bank's largest co-brand partnership. For more than 30 years, the strategic partnership has put an industry leading co-branded credit card in the wallet of millions of travelers and helped build various features of the airline's brand, including the famous Companion Fare.",
